===Etymology===
{{etyl|ML.|en}} {{m|la|dictionarium}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|dictionarius}}, from {{m|la|dictio||speaking}}, from {{m|la|dictus}}, perfect past participle of {{m|la|dƒ´c≈ç||speak}} + {{m|la|-arium||room, place}}.

