===Etymology===
From {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|encyclopaedia}}, from {{etyl|grc|en}} {{m|grc|·ºêŒ≥Œ∫œçŒ∫ŒªŒπŒøœÇ œÄŒ±ŒπŒ¥ŒµŒØŒ±||the circle of arts and sciences, curriculum}}, from {{m|grc|·ºêŒ≥Œ∫œçŒ∫ŒªŒπŒøœÇ||circular, rounded, round}}, from {{m|grc|Œ∫œçŒ∫ŒªŒøœÇ||circle}} + {{m|grc|œÄŒ±ŒπŒ¥ŒµŒØŒ±||the rearing of a child, education}}, from {{suffix|œÄŒ±ŒπŒ¥Œµœçœâ|ŒØ·æ±|t1=rear a child|nocat=yes|lang=grc}}, from {{m|grc|œÄŒ±·øñœÇ||child}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|Canada}} {{IPA|/…ônÀås…ô…™.kl…ôÀàpi.di…ô/|lang=en}}
* {{a|UK|US}} {{IPA|/…™nÀåsa…™.kl…ôÀàpi(Àê).di…ô/|lang=en}}
