===Etymology 1===
From {{etyl|grc|mul}} letter {{m|grc|Œë||alpha}}, derived from the {{etyl|phn|mul}} letter {{term|ê§Ä|tr= º||[[aleph]]|lang=phn}}.

====Pronunciation====
* {{IPA|/…ëÀê/|/a/|lang=mul}} {{qualifier|most languages}}

====Letter====
