==English==
The following tables show the [[Wiktionary:International Phonetic Alphabet|IPA]] and enPR/{{w|American Heritage Dictionary|AHD}} symbols which are used to represent the various sounds of the {{w|English language}}. The sounds of [[Received Pronunciation]] (RP, UK), [[General American]] pronunciation (GenAm, US), Australian English (AuE) and New Zealand English (NZE) are shown.

For vowels in other dialects, see Wikipedia's {{w|IPA chart for English}}.

:''An [[:Image:IPA Chart for English 2.png|image of an old version of these tables]] is available.''

===[[vowel|Vowels]]===
